  "texts": [
    "In feature extraction, YOLOv4 integrated numerous novel techniques, including CSPDarkNet53 and the mish activation function.",
    "Instead of FPN, SPP and PAN were employed to extend the perceptual field and conduct feature fusion.",
    "Overall, YOLOv4 is a significant improvement over YOLOv3 and has considerable technical value since it introduces the most recent research methods within the realm of deep learning for validation testing.",
    "The network topology of YOLOv5 can be broken down into four sections: input, backbone, neck, and prediction.",
    "This makes it quite similar to YOLOv4."
